{"tid":1930040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿「被感謝」 意外長斥華春瑩造假","createTime":"2020-03-17T09:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:12:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94baee0117822de7e2dc5e431996a52b12278a8a","tid":1930040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200317/LGZMVVQFX5KSVQZOIMI476ES4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2FLGZMVVQFX5KSVQZOIMI476ES4I%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=a172159a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2FLGZMVVQFX5KSVQZOIMI476ES4I%2F&h=ed1102f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200317/LGZMVVQFX5KSVQZOIMI476ES4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿「被感謝」 意外長斥華春瑩造假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200317/large/1584375554_a602.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200317%2Flarge%2F1584375554_a602.gif&h=6bce8448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意國外長迪馬約（右圖）指中國外交部發言人華春瑩（左圖）報假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩、趙立堅在Twitter大開「戰狼」模式，回擊外國對中國批評，宣傳中國「好事」。兩人近日在上載官媒拍攝的影像報道，顯示有疑似意大利播放中國國歌，及以意大利文「謝謝中國」。不過，意大利傳媒Linkiesta報道，意大利外交部長迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio）嚴正駁斥，指華春瑩在「散播假新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：28人英國返港不適送院<br />\n<br />\n指意市民播華國歌<br />\n<br />\n中國「輸出」武漢肺炎，與其有一帶一路合作的歐洲國家疫情嚴重；中方派出救援隊並捐贈物資，支援友好國家。華春瑩的Twitter上載《人民日報》報道，指記者在本月14日拍到有意大利市民播放中國國歌《義勇軍進行曲》，及一些意大利市民在家拍手片段，並指市民高叫「謝謝中國！」周圍市民鼓掌致意，「感人肺腑」。<br />\n<br />\n相關影像報道在各大官媒的YouTube頻道，包括CGTN、New China TV也有上載；國內媒體亦有報道事件。不過，Linkiesta報道指，意大利外交部長迪馬約否認事件，嚴正駁斥針對華春瑩在Twitter的帖文，指對方在「散播假新聞」，並指意大利還有其他緊急狀況要處理，請北京停止在這個時候散播假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容，華春瑩是中國外交部新聞司司長兼發言人，換句話說，「她是中國宣傳機構的領頭人之一，她的角色很明顯包含散播假新聞，如同她在官方推特的發言」。<br />\n<br />\nLinkiesta/Twitter"},{"pid":"41c904f17786b2dbdda03ee72e86a0800880ab31","tid":1930040,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"支那日日唔係叫爽就叫春，嘈撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa4b48cc54c16abd3968e81bca9158da821cf9e","tid":1930040,"uid":304856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"好少見歐洲國家會走出黎屌支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意大利真係俾人激到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599086ce3851fd1c369e3c4fc0940bfd2542a443","tid":1930040,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56834fc257b5e792856d537d6d60f9c50933e29","tid":1930040,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"依單野好多五毛話係fake news 係蘋果個ig瘋癲咁追擊 有冇人fc到"}]}